nodes.text: An Aqualish bounty hunter was present within the Mos Eisley Cantina when Zorba Desilijic Tiure learned that Leia Organa had murdered Zorba's son. Along with an unidentified Twi'lek, he ambushed Luke Skywalker, however, he was in turn killed, along with his Twi'lek companion during the attempt.
